      "settings": {
        "section_visibility": "always",
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"ui-feature-shell\">\n  <section class=\"ui-hero ui-wrap\">\n    <div class=\"ui-hero-copy\">\n      <p class=\"ui-kicker\">AAW</p>\n      <h1>What are Universal<em>In-Ear Monitors?</em></h1>\n      <p class=\"ui-dek\">A universal in-ear monitor is reference-grade sound, ready the moment it leaves our workshop. No impressions. No waiting. Choose your tips, slip them in, and meet the music exactly the way our engineers intended it. This is where the AAW universal experience begins.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"ui-hero-media\">\n      <img src=\"{{ 'a3h-lux-hero.jpg' | asset_img_url: '1024x' }}\" alt=\"AAW universal in-ear monitors — immediate, portable, and reference-grade\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1280\" loading=\"eager\">\n    </div>\n  </section>\n  <div class=\"ui-stat-strip\">\n    <div class=\"ui-wrap ui-stats\">\n      <div class=\"ui-stat\"><b>Ready to Wear</b><span>Universals leave the workshop in days. No appointments, no impressions, no lab queue — your monitor is packed, tested, and on its way the moment you order.</span></div>\n      <div class=\"ui-stat\"><b>Audition First</b><span>Hear any AAW model in person at our Singapore showroom or with an authorised dealer worldwide. Compare platforms side by side, then choose the signature that fits your music.</span></div>\n      <div class=\"ui-stat\"><b>A Range for Every Listener</b><span>From the accessible M20 to the tubeless Z07 flagship — AAW universals span every price tier, every architecture, every tuning preference. There is a right monitor for the way you listen.</span></div>\n      <div class=\"ui-stat\"><b>Reference in Your Pocket</b><span>Light, compact, and driven by any source. A universal IEM is a complete reference chain — studio-grade tuning, hand-built quality — that travels with you anywhere music does.</span></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>",
