    "ui_benefits": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "settings": {
        "section_visibility": "always",
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"ui-feature-shell\">\n  <section class=\"ui-section dark\">\n    <div class=\"ui-wrap\">\n      <div class=\"ui-section-head\">\n        <p class=\"ui-kicker\">Benefits</p>\n        <h2>Why Choose a Universal</h2>\n        <p>A custom monitor leads on isolation and fit. A universal trades that for immediacy, sharing, and a different kind of listening freedom — and there is a lot to be said for that.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"ui-benefit-grid\">\n        <div class=\"ui-benefit-card\">\n          <h3>Yours Within Days</h3>\n          <p>No lead time. No appointments. Order today and your monitor ships from our Singapore workshop within days — already tested, already listened to, already ready to be the next chapter of your listening life.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ui-benefit-card\">\n          <h3>Try Before You Decide</h3>\n          <p>You can hear a universal before owning it. Visit our showroom or an authorised dealer, listen to multiple AAW platforms back to back, and choose the signature that suits your ear. The demo is the product — and the product is the sound you take home.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ui-benefit-card\">\n          <h3>Made to Be Shared</h3>\n          <p>A custom fits one person. A universal can be passed to a bandmate, a partner, or a curious friend with a fresh pair of tips. It is the perfect introduction to AAW for the people you love — and the easiest way to begin your own collection.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ui-benefit-card\">\n          <h3>All the Sound, Less the Shell</h3>\n          <p>Universals don’t carry the labour of bespoke shell modelling and hand-finishing. The drivers, crossover, and tuning are identical to the custom equivalent — the savings come from the standardised shell. You pay for the sound, never for the form.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ui-benefit-card\">\n          <h3>Holds Its Value</h3>\n          <p>A universal serves any listener, so a used pair finds new owners easily. Clean the tips, fit a fresh cable, and it is as good as new for the person who comes next. Universals are an entry into reference audio that doesn’t disappear in resale.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ui-benefit-card\">\n          <h3>Tune the Fit Yourself</h3>\n          <p>Silicone for clarity. Foam for isolation. AAW LiquidMorph for a semi-custom seal that warms and conforms in minutes. Different tips change insertion depth, bass response, and even soundstage — putting a level of tonal control in your hands that a fixed shell can never offer.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n</div>",
