        "section_visibility": "always",
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"ui-feature-shell\">\n  <section class=\"ui-section\">\n    <div class=\"ui-wrap\">\n      <div class=\"ui-section-head\">\n        <p class=\"ui-kicker\">Comparison</p>\n        <h2>Universal vs Custom at a Glance</h2>\n        <p>Both formats share the same drivers, the same crossovers, the same tuning targets. The difference lives in the shell, the fit, and the way you live with them. Here is how they compare across the dimensions that matter.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"ui-compare-grid\">\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell header\"><h4>Feature</h4></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell header\"><h4>Universal IEM</h4></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell header\"><h4>Custom IEM</h4></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell label\"><span>Fit</span></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell highlight\"><p><b>Standardised shell with interchangeable tips; fits the widest range of ears well</b></p></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell\"><p>Moulded from your own impressions; an anatomical fit only you can wear</p></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell label\"><span>Lead Time</span></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell highlight\"><p><b>In stock; ships within days</b></p></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell\"><p>Approximately 2–4 weeks from receipt of impressions</p></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell label\"><span>Isolation</span></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell\"><p>−15 to −20 dB, depending on tip material and seal</p></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell highlight\"><p><b>Up to −26 dB with a full-shell passive seal</b></p></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell label\"><span>Sound Consistency</span></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell\"><p>Shifts subtly with tip choice and insertion depth</p></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell highlight\"><p><b>Fixed driver-to-eardrum distance; identical every session</b></p></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell label\"><span>Shareability</span></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell highlight\"><p><b>Easily shared — change tips for a fresh fit</b></p></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell\"><p>Fits one wearer; not designed to share</p></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell label\"><span>Resale Value</span></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell highlight\"><p><b>Strong second-hand market; ready for any listener</b></p></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell\"><p>Negligible; requires reshelling for a new owner</p></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell label\"><span>Personalisation</span></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell\"><p>Tips, cables, standard finishes</p></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell highlight\"><p><b>Shell colour, faceplate, artwork, engraving — yours to specify</b></p></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell label\"><span>Best For</span></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell highlight\"><p><b>First-time owners, side-by-side auditioning, backups, sharing, quick delivery</b></p></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell\"><p>Live performance, ultimate isolation, long-session comfort, deeply personal investment</p></div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n</div>",
