    "ui_products": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "settings": {
        "section_visibility": "always",
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"ui-feature-shell\">\n  <section class=\"ui-section\">\n    <div class=\"ui-wrap\">\n      <div class=\"ui-section-head\">\n        <p class=\"ui-kicker\">Our Range</p>\n        <h2>Recommended AAW Universal IEMs</h2>\n        <p>From the accessible M20 to the flagship Z07, every AAW universal shares one philosophy — musical, fatigue-free, and built to be lived with. Here are eight platforms, each a chapter in the AAW range.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"ui-product-grid\">\n        <a class=\"ui-product-card\" href=\"/products/z07-in-ear-monitor\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1313/3711/files/Z07-10.jpg?v=1776052779\" alt=\"AAW Z07 Tubeless Hybrid Reference Monitor\" loading=\"lazy\">\n          <div class=\"ui-product-body\">\n            <span class=\"ui-product-tag\">Flagship</span>\n            <h4>Z07</h4>\n            <p>Tubeless hybrid reference with FitMorph adaptive fit. Seven drivers, an expansive soundstage, and the kind of resolution that rewards your best recordings.</p>\n            <span class=\"ui-product-link\">View Z07 &rarr;</span>\n          </div>\n        </a>\n        <a class=\"ui-product-card\" href=\"/products/z06-universal-in-ear-monitor\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1313/3711/files/Z06-Web02.jpg?v=1718873976\" alt=\"AAW Z06 Hybrid In-Ear Monitor\" loading=\"lazy\">\n          <div class=\"ui-product-body\">\n            <span class=\"ui-product-tag\">Hybrid</span>\n            <h4>Z06</h4>\n            <p>Dual isobaric dynamic woofer paired with balanced armatures. Lush, vibrant, spacious — the musical all-rounder that asks nothing of the genre.</p>\n            <span class=\"ui-product-link\">View Z06 &rarr;</span>\n          </div>\n        </a>\n        <a class=\"ui-product-card\" href=\"/products/z05-auag-launch-edition\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1313/3711/files/z05-auag-twincore-switch-closeup.jpg?v=1779447818\" alt=\"AAW Z05 AuAg Launch Edition with TwinCore switch\" loading=\"lazy\">\n          <div class=\"ui-product-body\">\n            <span class=\"ui-product-tag\">TwinCore</span>\n            <h4>Z05 AuAg</h4>\n            <p>Five-driver hybrid with TwinCore switchable tuning. Two distinct signatures in a single, compact universal — the monitor that adapts to your evening.</p>\n            <span class=\"ui-product-link\">View Z05 AuAg &rarr;</span>\n          </div>\n        </a>\n        <a class=\"ui-product-card\" href=\"/products/advanced-acousticwerkes-w900-reference-universal-in-ear-monitor\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1313/3711/products/MockingbirdW900_1S.jpg?v=1547836547\" alt=\"AAW Mockingbird nine-driver hybrid reference\" loading=\"lazy\">\n          <div class=\"ui-product-body\">\n            <span class=\"ui-product-tag\">Reference</span>\n            <h4>Mockingbird</h4>\n            <p>Nine-driver hybrid reference, available as both universal and custom. The same acoustic engine — your choice of fit, your investment, your way.</p>\n            <span class=\"ui-product-link\">View Mockingbird &rarr;</span>\n          </div>\n        </a>\n        <a class=\"ui-product-card\" href=\"/products/halcyon-electrostatic-hybrid-in-ear-monitor\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1313/3711/files/HalcyonV6frontal.2.png?v=1690955341\" alt=\"AAW Halcyon electrostatic hybrid IEM\" loading=\"lazy\">\n          <div class=\"ui-product-body\">\n            <span class=\"ui-product-tag\">Electrostatic</span>\n            <h4>Halcyon</h4>\n            <p>Electrostatic hybrid with rare treble extension. A specialist monitor for listeners who want air, detail, and a sense of openness above all.</p>\n            <span class=\"ui-product-link\">View Halcyon &rarr;</span>\n          </div>\n        </a>\n        <a class=\"ui-product-card\" href=\"/products/ash-universal-in-ear-monitor\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1313/3711/products/ASH_1.jpg?v=1547656852\" alt=\"AAW ASH hybrid in-ear monitor\" loading=\"lazy\">\n          <div class=\"ui-product-body\">\n            <span class=\"ui-product-tag\">Hybrid</span>\n            <h4>ASH</h4>\n            <p>Balanced hybrid with a natural midrange and controlled low end. A refined daily companion built for the long listen, not the quick impression.</p>\n            <span class=\"ui-product-link\">View ASH &rarr;</span>\n          </div>\n        </a>\n        <a class=\"ui-product-card\" href=\"/products/advanced-acousticwerkes-a3h-universal-in-ear-monitor\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1313/3711/files/A3M4.2.png?v=1737910239\" alt=\"AAW A3H+ Lux three-driver hybrid\" loading=\"lazy\">\n          <div class=\"ui-product-body\">\n            <span class=\"ui-product-tag\">Entry Hybrid</span>\n            <h4>A3H+ Lux</h4>\n            <p>Three-driver hybrid platform — the gateway into AAW hybrid sound. Warm, engaging, and quietly accomplished far beyond its price.</p>\n            <span class=\"ui-product-link\">View A3H+ Lux &rarr;</span>\n          </div>\n        </a>\n        <a class=\"ui-product-card\" href=\"/products/m20-universal-in-ear-monitor\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1313/3711/files/M20_1.jpg?v=1690954421\" alt=\"AAW M20 dual armature in-ear monitor\" loading=\"lazy\">\n          <div class=\"ui-product-body\">\n            <span class=\"ui-product-tag\">Dual BA</span>\n            <h4>M20</h4>\n            <p>Dual balanced armature monitor. Clean, accurate, and accessible — the most affordable entry into the AAW tuning philosophy, with no compromise on tone.</p>\n            <span class=\"ui-product-link\">View M20 &rarr;</span>\n          </div>\n        </a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n</div>",
