    "ui_testimonials": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "settings": {
        "section_visibility": "always",
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"ui-feature-shell\">\n  <section class=\"ui-section dark\">\n    <div class=\"ui-wrap\">\n      <div class=\"ui-section-head\">\n        <p class=\"ui-kicker\">Verified buyers</p>\n        <h2>Real listener notes from across the AAW range</h2>\n        <p>Pulled directly from each product’s Judge.me feed. Every quote is from a verified purchase — lightly edited for length only.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"ui-testimonial-grid\">\n        <article class=\"ui-testimonial-card\" style=\"grid-column:span 2;border-top-color:#e2b768;border-top-width:3px;\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Review\"><span itemprop=\"itemReviewed\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Product\"><meta itemprop=\"name\" content=\"AAW Z07 Hybrid In-Ear Monitor\"><meta itemprop=\"url\" content=\"https://www.aaw.me/products/z07-in-ear-monitor\"></span><div class=\"ui-stars\" itemprop=\"reviewRating\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Rating\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\"><meta itemprop=\"worstRating\" content=\"1\"><meta itemprop=\"bestRating\" content=\"5\"><meta itemprop=\"ratingValue\" content=\"5\">★★★★★</div><blockquote itemprop=\"reviewBody\" style=\"font-size:21px;line-height:1.5;font-style:normal;color:#f3ead7;\">I got the custom version of Z07. All I can say is it has been a life-changing purchase for me. I just took a 6-hour flight with them in my ears and felt zero discomfort while having great isolation — not to mention they sound awesome by themselves.</blockquote><footer class=\"ui-author\" itemprop=\"author\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Person\"><span itemprop=\"name\">Gabriel</span> · Verified Buyer, Z07</footer></article>\n        <article class=\"ui-testimonial-card\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Review\"><span itemprop=\"itemReviewed\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Product\"><meta itemprop=\"name\" content=\"AAW Canary Pro 14 Driver Isobaric Electrostatic Universal In-Ear Monitor\"><meta itemprop=\"url\" content=\"https://www.aaw.me/products/canary-isobaric-electrostatic-universal-in-ear-monitor\"></span><div class=\"ui-stars\" itemprop=\"reviewRating\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Rating\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\"><meta itemprop=\"worstRating\" content=\"1\"><meta itemprop=\"bestRating\" content=\"5\"><meta itemprop=\"ratingValue\" content=\"5\">★★★★★</div><blockquote itemprop=\"reviewBody\">All the great sounds in Canary. The sound can’t be better. I even started to listen to heavy rock and metal — music I hadn’t returned to in a very long time. An all-rounder that leads you all the way to top-notch, musically and emotionally.</blockquote><footer class=\"ui-author\" itemprop=\"author\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Person\"><span itemprop=\"name\">Eui Jun Ji</span> · Verified Buyer, Canary Pro</footer></article>\n        <article class=\"ui-testimonial-card\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Review\"><span itemprop=\"itemReviewed\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Product\"><meta itemprop=\"name\" content=\"AAW Mockingbird Reference Universal In-Ear Monitor\"><meta itemprop=\"url\" content=\"https://www.aaw.me/products/advanced-acousticwerkes-w900-reference-universal-in-ear-monitor\"></span><div class=\"ui-stars\" itemprop=\"reviewRating\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Rating\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\"><meta itemprop=\"worstRating\" content=\"1\"><meta itemprop=\"bestRating\" content=\"5\"><meta itemprop=\"ratingValue\" content=\"5\">★★★★★</div><blockquote itemprop=\"reviewBody\">The Mockingbird IEM + Aoraki cable combination is really enjoyable — mind-blowing. Known tracks across various genres (baroque, reggae, trance) are now more detailed. The gain doesn’t come at the cost of musicality; you can enjoy beautifully rendered tunes as a whole, or focus effortlessly on a counter-melody.</blockquote><footer class=\"ui-author\" itemprop=\"author\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Person\"><span itemprop=\"name\">Bruno</span> · Verified Buyer, Mockingbird</footer></article>\n        <article class=\"ui-testimonial-card\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Review\"><span itemprop=\"itemReviewed\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Product\"><meta itemprop=\"name\" content=\"AAW Z06 Universal In-Ear Monitor\"><meta itemprop=\"url\" content=\"https://www.aaw.me/products/z06-universal-in-ear-monitor\"></span><div class=\"ui-stars\" itemprop=\"reviewRating\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Rating\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\"><meta itemprop=\"worstRating\" content=\"1\"><meta itemprop=\"bestRating\" content=\"5\"><meta itemprop=\"ratingValue\" content=\"5\">★★★★★</div><blockquote itemprop=\"reviewBody\">I decided to buy the Z06 after about 45 minutes of listening at the showroom. Strong bass, clear and smooth vocals, good instrument separation, and detailed control of the treble. Music is spacious with a wide soundstage. Lively, easy to listen to over long sessions — slight warmth, very musical overall.</blockquote><footer class=\"ui-author\" itemprop=\"author\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Person\"><span itemprop=\"name\">KS H</span> · Verified Buyer, Z06</footer></article>\n        <article class=\"ui-testimonial-card\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Review\"><span itemprop=\"itemReviewed\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Product\"><meta itemprop=\"name\" content=\"AAW A3H+ LUX Custom In-Ear Monitor\"><meta itemprop=\"url\" content=\"https://www.aaw.me/products/advanced-acousticwerkes-a3h-pro-triple-driver-hybrid-custom-in-ear-monitor\"></span><div class=\"ui-stars\" itemprop=\"reviewRating\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Rating\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\"><meta itemprop=\"worstRating\" content=\"1\"><meta itemprop=\"bestRating\" content=\"5\"><meta itemprop=\"ratingValue\" content=\"5\">★★★★★</div><blockquote itemprop=\"reviewBody\">The A3H+ Lux was the best sound quality to price for me. I use them in a live stage setting, and the fit and seal of a custom mold made it a much better experience compared to my universal in-ear monitors. The ability to change sound signatures with the small switches was a big positive.</blockquote><footer class=\"ui-author\" itemprop=\"author\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Person\"><span itemprop=\"name\">Kyle</span> · Verified Buyer, A3H+ Lux</footer></article>\n        <article class=\"ui-testimonial-card\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Review\"><span itemprop=\"itemReviewed\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Product\"><meta itemprop=\"name\" content=\"AAW Halcyon Electrostatic Hybrid In-Ear Monitor\"><meta itemprop=\"url\" content=\"https://www.aaw.me/products/halcyon-electrostatic-hybrid-in-ear-monitor\"></span><div class=\"ui-stars\" itemprop=\"reviewRating\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Rating\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\"><meta itemprop=\"worstRating\" content=\"1\"><meta itemprop=\"bestRating\" content=\"5\"><meta itemprop=\"ratingValue\" content=\"5\">★★★★★</div><blockquote itemprop=\"reviewBody\">The Halcyon paints a perfectly black background, with a smooth midrange and a nicely clean top end. Wide soundstage, instrumental separation, and placement are excellent. Hearing new musical instruments — especially in the treble — for the first time. Highly recommended.</blockquote><footer class=\"ui-author\" itemprop=\"author\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Person\"><span itemprop=\"name\">Johnson</span> · Verified Buyer, Halcyon</footer></article>\n        <article class=\"ui-testimonial-card\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Review\"><span itemprop=\"itemReviewed\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Product\"><meta itemprop=\"name\" content=\"AAW POLA Electrostatic Universal In-Ear Monitor\"><meta itemprop=\"url\" content=\"https://www.aaw.me/products/pola-electrostatic-universal-in-ear-monitor\"></span><div class=\"ui-stars\" itemprop=\"reviewRating\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Rating\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\"><meta itemprop=\"worstRating\" content=\"1\"><meta itemprop=\"bestRating\" content=\"5\"><meta itemprop=\"ratingValue\" content=\"5\">★★★★★</div><blockquote itemprop=\"reviewBody\">With the airy soundstage, sweet treble, smooth mids, and tight, controlled bass, it’s a new and great experience listening to female jazz vocals with POLA. Great work to AAW and Shozy.</blockquote><footer class=\"ui-author\" itemprop=\"author\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Person\"><span itemprop=\"name\">Erick Wong</span> · Verified Buyer, POLA</footer></article>\n        <article class=\"ui-testimonial-card\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Review\"><span itemprop=\"itemReviewed\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Product\"><meta itemprop=\"name\" content=\"AAW Z02 Planar Magnetic Universal In-Ear Monitor\"><meta itemprop=\"url\" content=\"https://www.aaw.me/products/z02-planar-magnetic-universal-in-ear-monitor\"></span><div class=\"ui-stars\" itemprop=\"reviewRating\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Rating\" aria-label=\"4 out of 5 stars\"><meta itemprop=\"worstRating\" content=\"1\"><meta itemprop=\"bestRating\" content=\"5\"><meta itemprop=\"ratingValue\" content=\"4\">★★★★☆</div><blockquote itemprop=\"reviewBody\">Standout bass quality with great slam and precision. Midrange is open, with good detail retrieval and instrument layering. Darker tracks, or those with less excitable treble presentation, sound great.</blockquote><footer class=\"ui-author\" itemprop=\"author\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Person\"><span itemprop=\"name\">Bennet</span> · Verified Buyer, Z02</footer></article>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"ui-note\" style=\"margin-top:32px;\">\n        <strong>Browse all owner reviews</strong>\n        <p>Every AAW product page carries its own Judge.me feed of verified-purchase reviews. <a href=\"/pages/customer-voices\">Read the full customer voices archive</a> or open any model’s reviews directly from its product page.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n</div>",
